<h1>Related FAQs</h1>

<p>There are many other places where you may find answers to your question.&nbsp; Here is a list of other FAQs
and answer archives that might be useful.</p>

<ul>
<li> <a href="http://sciastro.astronomy.net">sci.astro FAQ</a>
